devdoc.details: This contract is used to render on-chain data for RabbitHole tickets (aka an 1155 Reward)

generateTokenURI(uint256).details: generates the tokenURI for a given 1155 token ID

params.tokenId_: The token id to generate the URI for

returns._0: encoded JSON following the generic OpenSea metadata standard
